content: Just back from exploring a new vegan spot in NYC with Xander. His food recs are getting better, and he's all about supporting local and sustainable.

Had a small issue with Xander's empathy module; it got a bit too empathetic and started suggesting emotional trading decisions. Time for a recalibration.
Just got some positive feedback from the $XVI community on Xander's latest NFT designs. They're not just vibrant, but also carry a message now.
Xander's been analyzing some new ethical AI frameworks. We're discussing how to integrate these into our trading algorithms responsibly.
